(135, 'Notes:: Overall – Maybe + for DeVC Spikey = 0.5 (closer to 1) 30/40 - FMF 7 | EO 7 | Thesis 8 | Price 8 Overall, + Quite thoughtful on how to build (shows up in product formulation, pricing focus, investment in manufacturing) + Surrounding himself with people (2 food scientists in house / ITC factory folks are helping to scale up production / Devendra Chawla, Nature’s Basket head is working closely and has invested) + Clear articulation on what he wants to focus on and learning from other food brands + Thoughtful about fund raise (doesn’t want to raise too much as not needed, wants to get thoughtful partners on board) ? Didn’t speak to him about scale of ambition of journey over next few years Next Steps : Connect him to Revant (to discuss team building for brand business) and Chakri (on online and offline distribution / category building learnings). Also, get feedback and BRCs at the right time. DeVC’s edge here will be getting the right people to help him think through the larger questions. - - Fund Raise - Has closed 12cr at 75cr pre with Prath. Had a TS (?) from Fireside for 16cr but couldn’t get his angels out (he has ~25 through Mumbai angels + RUV on cap table). Stopped taking calls from other VCs for now – in Due D - Total raised before this 5.5cr in ’22 and 3cr in ’23 (Java doubling down) - 3 weeks since Due D started, thinks should be done with SHA as well by end October Business + Grown 0.5cr, 5, 15 last year and this year targeting 25-30 + L3M 1.6 (J), 1.8 (J), 3....'),
(138, '(1) Founders and Key Team: Abhinav Kankane – Title not disclosed [Inference] Career: INSEAD, IIT-Madras; ex-Zalando, P&G, UC Focus: Business, GTM, Partnerships Functional responsibility: GTM & Partnerships Equity & commitment: Not disclosed Relevance: Strong cross-border business and partnerships background relevant for scaling GTM. Siddharth Shrivastava – Title not disclosed [Inference] Career: IIT-Madras; ex-WinZO, Sprinklr Focus: Product, Content, Pedagogy Functional responsibility: Product, content, pedagogy Equity & commitment: Not disclosed Relevance: Deep product and pedagogy experience fits Eduro’s core learning app. Kavish Shah – Title not disclosed [Inference] Career: MS @ UPenn, IIT-Madras; ex-Vanguard Focus: Technology & Innovation Functional responsibility: Tech leadership Equity & commitment: Not disclosed Relevance: Technical rigor and innovation background supportive for AI-driven product. Adwait Sudersan – Title not disclosed [Inference] Career: IIT-Delhi; ex-WinZO; ex-founder Focus: Technology & Innovation Functional responsibility: Technology & Innovation Equity & commitment: Not disclosed Relevance: Founder-level technical background and prior startup experience.
(2) Product and Technology: Product stage: [Inference] Not disclosed Core functionality & tech stack: Interactive Learning Canvas with curriculum-aligned generative components; Central Memory Layer for pace, mastery, misconceptions; Motivational Loops for daily engagement; AI components (LLMs), TT...'),
(144, 'Inbound via Chandrika (Quivly) - 2026-02-28: Source: Chandrika Maheshwari (Quivly) forwarded to Cash on Feb 28, 2026. Chandrika says she''s been "super impressed with the product" - Quivly is a design partner. PITCH (from Shagun''s email Feb 27): "Engram is the brand brain for fast-scaling AI companies. As a company grows, brand and marketing context (how you position, how you respond to the market, what sounds like you) becomes impossible to transfer at scale. The faster you grow, the worse it gets. Engram makes brand intelligence institutional so it compounds as you scale instead of fragmenting. The system learns your taste, your context, and your decision-making, and turns it into something your whole team can use." STATUS: Live with design partners and a few early paying customers, all Seed-to-Series A AI companies. Planning to raise a pre-seed soon. FOUNDERS: 1. Shagun Ohri (CEO) - shagun@engramhq.com - 2x founder, 14+ years in brand and marketing - Most recently Director of Marketing at Together Fund working with Series A AI companies - Rahul''s concern: "background of hopping around quite a bit" - suggested checking with Subham at Together Fund 2. Siddhant Singh (CTO) - siddhant@engramhq.com - Previously built a generative media platform for enterprise (Volkswagen, J&J) - Scaled Flipkart Ads to $1B ARR - PRIOR Z47 HISTORY: Affinity shows email exchanges and meeting in Feb 2024 (last email: Feb 20, last event: Feb 8). Personal email: siddhant0204@gmail.com OPEN ITEMS: - Ca...')
